test_even_range:
assert [6, 8, 10] == [8, 10]
  At index 0 diff: 6 != 8
  Left contains one more item: 10
  Full diff:
  - [8, 10]
  + [6, 8, 10]
  ?  +++
test_large_range:
assert [3, 4, 5] == [4, 5]
  At index 0 diff: 3 != 4
  Left contains one more item: 5
  Full diff:
  - [4, 5]
  + [3, 4, 5]
  ?  +++
